{"tid":2087020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【FF大軍】認真，你想住喺個點嘅香港？","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:58:26.000Z","uid":50983,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"133aac51332a258160190c59303122c68e36d320","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cjkhca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cjkhca.jpg&h=475e8a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極權政府最怕嘅係人民嘅想像。<br />\n想像給予人信念、勇氣、付諸實行嘅動力，<br />\n集結大家去打破高牆嘅威壓、被消失嘅恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n襯我地仲有時間喺連登講野，<br />\n大家不如一齊形容下自己<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理想中嘅香港</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你想住喺個點嘅香港？<br />\n光復咗嘅香港係點？<br />\n自由嘅香港係點？<br />\n想自己同下一代生活喺一個點嘅香港？<br />\n希望香港係點嘅屋企、城市？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後嘅日子我地要抱住呢個想像迎難以上，<br />\n緊記我地共同嘅想像，記住香港嘅可能性，<br />\n日日FF下我地想要嘅香港，直到有日我地可以一齊建造呢個城市。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Ideas are bulletproof.</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n琴晚post得太夜，想今晚重post過，<br />\n有啲人share咗喺到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2085176/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2085176/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"41e35b6abc5354ee2b0d40bf53f5ef8314838f79","tid":2087020,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"再推！聽日街頭見！<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立！"},{"pid":"126eb9f91e7f53123141a267f6aa3252d5cd292a","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"我想要香港擁有自己鮮明嘅文化，電視會有好多視點咁嘅政治人物對罵嘅節目，小朋友喺學校會學識發表自己意見、理性思考，但想做港豬時都可以心安理得做港豬。"},{"pid":"0f917ec46d19cbb600f754d8ec59d00711d247b8","tid":2087020,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3b668c3eac26694a8867ac404e6ed8be1d6b37","tid":2087020,"uid":21143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"聽日見啦"},{"pid":"c9e5fa12ed035f4426bd546536a0440501529108","tid":2087020,"uid":19817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"},{"pid":"90addf84aa1448ce99b73d559c8105e33b8d52b4","tid":2087020,"uid":307203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"有百花齊放嘅傳媒<br />\n<br />\n同有獨立自主嘅香港電台"},{"pid":"d4e45787cb036320ead4b36bf8b4b62d7bde4dab","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"自推返"},{"pid":"24a23fef28d30f0687e02796ae05b74830e96a07","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"知道自己想要咩先可以打得長久"},{"pid":"5eb2263b4a3f241b1034f443d5f4f0485f9c3e2c","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"琴日有人話<br />\n「可以踩單車去到全港任何地方嘅香港」"},{"pid":"2f0bb574e7b842b308657c5312dc3bc7953e0d0b","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"有人話<br />\n「工時正常化 整體生活負擔成本得到降低 社會人民公義得到保障」"},{"pid":"fe7f503aa7762d3b562959f533801bc80dea3853","tid":2087020,"uid":50983,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"有人話<br />\n「港人治港 港人優先<br />\n收緊居留權 政策唔一定要正確 但市民有不滿 政府會改<br />\n減少人口 停止酷刑聲請 商場唔再係倒模商場 教育唔需要再有愛國慨念 商鋪同居住單位空置稅極大離譜毀滅性地大幅增加<br />\n官員議員只可以有單一香港藉 監警會由巿民定期選出」"},{"pid":"9553238d98c4